hdf5r

Class for HDF5 property list for dataset access

It inherits all functions of the H5P-class.

Value

Object of class H5P_DATASET_ACCESS.

Methods

set_chunk_cache(rdcc_nslots = -1, rdcc_nbytes = -1, rdcc_w0 = -1)

This function implements the HDF5-API function H5Pset_chunk_cache. Please see the documentation at https://www.hdfgroup.org/HDF5/doc/RM/RM_H5P.html#Property-SetChunkCache for details.

get_chunk_cache()

This function implements the HDF5-API function H5Pget_chunk_cache. Please see the documentation at https://www.hdfgroup.org/HDF5/doc/RM/RM_H5P.html#Property-GetChunkCache for details.
